      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "DARING BANDIT (8) turned in a fair 5th placed finish last time at Traralgon over 425m (24.71). Has placed a couple of times at this track. Can discover winning form. DIAMANTINA PEAR (1) is yet to miss the frame this course and distance. Is suited by the inside draw. Latest effort finished 3rd over 450m at Warrnambool beaten 4.5 lengths (25.58) behind Paw Revy in a Grade 5 on May 14. Looks a key player on best form. MORE THAN WORDS (2) was safely held last time out, finishing fifth at Traralgon over 425m behind Sharni's Secret (24.54) in a Grade 4/5. Consistent performer from this draw with a win and two minor placings to her credit. Better than the latest run and deserves another chance.",
